    "## 🧪 试题一：用 DataFrame 复刻 SQL 窗口函数\n",
    "\n",
    "**🌍 业务场景**：\n",
    "在 SQL 中，找出用户“最新一次登录日期”并过滤出最新日期的行为极其容易 (`ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY user_id ORDER BY visit_date DESC) = 1`)。\n",
    "\n",
    "**📝 你的任务**：\n",
    "给你包含了多条重复 `user_id` 的访问明细表 `df_visit`，请用一行代码找出每个用户**最后一次**访问的**完整明细行**。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "\n",
    "df_visit = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "    'user_id': [1, 1, 2, 2, 2, 3],\n",
    "    'visit_date': pd.to_datetime(['2023-01-01', '2023-01-05', '2023-01-02', '2023-01-08', '2023-01-04', '2023-01-10']),\n",
    "    'page_view': [10, 5, 12, 8, 20, 15]\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "# ==================\n",
    "# 你的代码写在这里：\n",
    "df_latest = ...\n",
    "\n",
    "# ==================\n",
    "\n",
    "# ---------------------\n",
    "# 💡 面试官满分答案：\n",
    "# df_latest = df_visit.sort_values('visit_date').drop_duplicates('user_id', keep='last')\n",
    "# 不要用 groupby 然后 merge，太低效。sort + drop_duplicates 是 Pandas 里替代 ROW_NUMBER 最优雅的大杀器。"
   ]
